title: [Gyldemar Forest, Winding Trail]
description: A stiff breeze sweeps the fallen leaves from the path to reveal irregular and deeply weathered blocks of native stone.  Subtle colors in the rock set off the brilliant viridian hue of the moss which grows between the stones.  A less defined path, perhaps an animal track, branches off to the southwest.
